function [m,v,q50]=gaussstat(param);% gaussstat                 - Mean, variance and median of the Gaussian distribution (Jan 1,2001)%% Return the mean,variance and median for a Gaussian% distribution with specified mean and variance parameters.%% SYNTAX :%% [m,v,q50]=gaussstat(param);%% INPUT :%% param    1 by 2   parameters of the Gaussian distribution, where :%                   param(1) is the mean of the distribution,%                   param(2) is the variance of the distribution.%% OUTPUT :%% m        scalar   mean of the distribution.% v        scalar   variance of the distribution.% q50      scalar   mediane of the distribution.m=param(1);v=param(2);q50=param(1);